DEFINITIONS

"Software" means the Provable AI source code, documentation, tools, and
associated files published at github.com/futureaihub/provable-ai.

"Commercial Use" means any use of the Software in a product, service,
or workflow that is offered to third parties, generates revenue, or is
used in a production environment.

"Evaluation Use" means running the Software locally, reading the source
code, running tests, and assessing whether the Software meets your
requirements, for non-commercial purposes only.

"Zorynex" means the legal entity operating under the name Zorynex,
contactable at hanif@zorynex.co.

