GRANT OF RIGHTS — EVALUATION USE

Subject to the terms of this Licence, Zorynex grants you a limited,
non-exclusive, non-transferable, royalty-free right to:

1. View, clone, and read the Software source code.
2. Run the Software locally for Evaluation Use only.
3. Run the Software's test suite for Evaluation Use only.
4. Use the independent verification tools (cli.py, offline_verify.py,
   verify_core.py, verify_proof.py) to verify proof artifacts generated
   by a licensed deployment of the Software.
5. Modify the Software for personal Evaluation Use only, provided that
   modified versions are not distributed.

